Receive instant system alerts as contract terminations approach to properly assess key factors and avoid the all too common evergreen lease state.

LEASETRAX

Protect Your Lease Portfolio With Our Services Coupled With Industry Leading Software For Immediate ROI And Staff Leverage

About Us

LeaseTrax is a full-service lease administration company, coupled with latest software technology that allows our clients to track, manage, and manipulate lease reporting with accurate and detailed view summaries.  

Whether you are in need of an automated solution or an end to end Enterprise management of your lease lifecycle, LeaseTrax can meet your organizational needs. We provide a holistic approach to lease administration, leveraging a single centralized repository designed and customized to tailor your specific business requirements. 

Learn More

Shaping The Future Of Lease Administration

Allow LeaseTrax to create a seamless lease administration process through a combination of administration expertise and user-friendly software solutions. 

Improve Efficiency

Manage enterprise wide lease activity with a user friendly automated lease administration process

Increase Visibility

Avoid sub-par decisions in crucial areas due to inconsistent communication and poor visibility. Our solution allows for visibility at the individual lease level and the entire lease portfolio

Optimize Performance

Maximize the full potential of your portfolio by allowing us to create a cost efficient and seamless process for an overall accurate lease management

Why LeaseTrax?

Administration

Let our lease administration experts provide a full service management of your global real estate lease portfolios, tailored to your requirements.

Cloud Based

Support your most critical team. Define custom process flow for your Sales activity, with unlimited access. The support you need, automatically accessible and just one click away. 

Reporting & Analytics

Extract and analyze critical dates and financial forecast to help better understand and improve your lease portfolio. 

Full Integration

Seamlessly intergrate within your current CRM application and legacy systems. If in need of Modules, no worries, simply ask and we shall provide.

Compliance

We provide leasing services for Enterprise Organizations seeking to remain compliant with and benefit from new leasing standards. Designed to keep up with current and new standards. (IFRS 16 & ASC 842) 

Cost Reduction

Avoid the unecessary evergreeen cost due to past terms and lost assets. Let our experts identify your overcharges and reduce your financial exposure.

item.title: About
item.dc:creator: Marboite30
item.content:encoded:
Welcome to LeaseTrax

Take Full Control of Your Lease Portfolio

Request Demo

About Us

The LeaseTrax team of Lease Administration experts help man age your global lease portfolios, regardless of portfolio size and complexity. Lease Administration with LeaseTrax is designed to provide a single repository for all pertinent lease information, with a solution to the entire lifecycle, including procurement, approvals, data abstraction, and compliance. Our team of experts can design the optimal approach to your organizations business requirements, regardless of lease portfolio size and complexity. Let our team consolidate and manage all of the pertinent details in an effort to identify hidden gaps, overcharges, and reporting compliance issues, ultimately reducing your financial exposure. Contact us today to learn more about how we can solve your lease administration issues.

item.title: Solutions
item.dc:creator: Marboite30
item.content:encoded:
Take Control of Your Lease Portfolio

Effectively Manage Enterprise-wide Leasing Activity With Our Services and A User Friendly Customized Software Solution 

Efficiency

Manage enterprise wide lease activity with a user friendly automated lease administration process

Visibility

Avoid sub-par decisions in crucial areas due to inconsistent communication and poor visibility. Our solution allows for visibility at the individual lease level and the entire lease portfolio

Optimization

Maximize the full potential of your portfolio by allowing us to create a cost efficient and seamless process for an overall accurate lease management

LeaseTrax Admin Services

Lease Review

Our team will draft, review, and revise various types of transactional agreements in connection with your organizations real estate management and leasing portfolio.

Accounts Receivable/Accounts Payable

AR/AP services, which include the management of outgoing bills and invoices on behalf of your organization. In addition, ensuring all payments are sent accurately and punctually while remaining in accordance with your company policy

Compliance

We work with company departments, i.e., accounting and asset acquisitions/dispositions as necessary, to ensure consistent communication across the entire organization and ensure compliance.

Data Abstraction

We'll take overall control of original lease documentation and maintenance of master lease files. We receive and set up all lease documents into our software and assist with abstracting important data of lease agreements.

Onboarding

Improve lease onboarding process through LeaseTrax's database, leveraging concise checkpoints from initiation to final approved assets. 

Set-up

Formalize your lease set-up with our integrated solution that speeds up processess and allows for efficient communication across your organization.

Operation

Full exposure to your global lease portfolios throughout the life of the lease, with a user-friendly dashboard and access to key dates, asset values, and maintenance records.

termination

Receive instant system alerts as contract terminations approach to properly assess key factors and avoid the all too common evergreen lease state. 

Discover More

The LeaseTrax team of administration experts help manage your global lease portfolios, regardless of portfolio size and complexity. Lease Administration with LeaseTrax is designed to provide a single repository for all pertinent lease information, with a solution to the entire lifecycle; including procurement, approvals, data abstraction, and compliance. Our team of experts can design the optimal approach to your organizations lease and business requirements. Let our team consolidate and manage all of the pertinent details in an effort to identify hidden gaps, overcharges, and compliance issues, ultimately reducing your financial exposure. Contact us today to learn more about how we can provide immediate value to your organizations lease portfolio.

Learn More

item.dc:creator: Marboite30
item.content:encoded:
• Edit

Why LeaseTrax?

  • Edit

Administration

Single centralized repository, designed to create an improved managment process of the lease lifecycle. 

  • Edit

Cloud Based

Support your most critical team. Define custom process flow for your Sales activity, with unlimited access. The support you need, automatically accessible and just one click away. 

  • Edit

Reporting & Analytics

Extract and analyze critical dates and financial forecast to help better understand and improve your lease portfolio. 

  • Edit

Full Integration

Seamlessly intergrate within your current CRM application, billing, and Inventory. If in need of Modules, no worries, simply ask and we shall provide.

  • Edit

Compliance

Leasing services for Enterprise Organizations seeking to remain compliant with and benefit from new leasing standards. Designed to keep up with current and new complaince standards. (IFRS 16 & ASC 842) 

  • Edit

Cost Reduction

Avoid the unecessary evergreeen cost due to past terms and lost assets

item.title: About Us
item.dc:creator: Marboite30
item.content:encoded:
• Edit

About Us

Lease Administration by LeaseTrax is designed from the ground up to provide a single, unifed repository for all relevant lease information. The solution addresses the full lease lifecycle, including approvals and procurement, lease vs buy analysis, data abstraction, and each change event including and up to terminations, extensions, and asset retirement. A single point of entry is used to collect all lease data into the unified repository, using extensible data collection formats to flexibly capture custom attributes depending on your business processes.

The LeaseTrax Lease Administration solution also allows users to .

 

The LeaseTrax team of Lease Administration experts help man age your global lease portfolios, regardless of portfolio size and complexity. Lease Administration with LeaseTrax is designed to provide a single repository for all pertinent lease information, with a solution to the entire lifecycle, including procurement, approvals, data abstraction, and compliance. Our team of experts can design the optimal approach to your organizations business requirements, regardless of lease portfolio size and complexity. We will 

 

deliver significant cost savings in managing your global real estate and equipment lease portfolios. Our lease administration and compliance services are tailored to your needs, no matter the size of your company’s portfolio. Let us help design the optimal approach to your lease administration requirements. 

Lease Abstraction experts help you consolidate and manage all the necessary information to identify overcharges, proactively reduce your financial exposure, and comply with reporting requirements. Talk to us, we can tailor an approach that fits your company’s business requirements.

Our service engagements always begin with critical listening, without a bias for any service or technology application.  Our solutions appropriately blend people, process, and technology, while considering the unique culture and operating realities of each client. Our solutions incorporate the best prevailing non-proprietary technology, allowing for an intuitive and portable means of structuring and sharing data across geographic regions.  We have a professional staff . Contact us today to learn more about what we can do for you.
